Tizmekt tazegzawt d [[aɣersiw]] ameqqran yettwassnen yakk ig ddren deg [[tagnit|tegnit]] ama tura neɣ deg yal tallit yezrkn,<ref name="des"/> ma d [[adinaẓur]] ameqqran yakk yettwassnen iga d [[Arjintinusawrus]] yeddren deg tallit n [[tudralmast]]. [[Azuk|Azuk-is]] d win yellan yettawaṭ ɣer 90 n iṭunnen,<ref>(Spanish) Bonaparte J, Coria R (1993). Un nuevo y gigantesco sauropodo titanosaurio de la Formacion Rio Limay (Albiano-Cenomaniano) de la Provincia del Neuquen, Argentina. ''Ameghiniana'' '''30''' (3): 271–282</ref> ayen i d-immalen d akken d tizmekt tazegzawt i d-t-yugaren s waṭas. Dɣa azuk n tezmekt tazegzawt d win yemrayen i [[akat|wakat]] s usrag n ubleɣ-is meqqren s waṭas. Akken i tga tegnit yakk d tzemkin timeqqṛanin niden i d-[[agmar|gemmren]] inegmaren, [[awtem|iwetmen]] n tezmekt tazegzawt werjin ttwaktan yakk, maca ttwagzamen ɣer igezzumen meẓẓiyen sin akin ad yifrir (ad yishil) wakat-nsen, dɣa anecta yeǧǧa isazalen n wazuk i d-ttafen d wid i d-itteffaɣen ur wwiṭen ara ɣer wazuk-is imdetti (n tidett) acku tizmekt mi ara ad tettwagzem tzelli (tesṛuḥay) aṭas seg [[amazzal|yimazzalen-is]] d [[idammen]]-is 

Tizemkin tizegzawin yettidiren deg [[agaraw Aṭlasi|ugaraw anaṭlas]] d [[Agaraw Amelwi|ugaraw Amelwi]] ttilint meẓẓiy-it ɣef tid yettidiren deg [[yideggan yudsen ɣer tizgelt n unẓul]], anda i d-ttujerden wazuken igan gar n 150 alamma d 170 n iṭunnen i tzemkin yessawaṭen di teɣzi ɣef 27 m, dɣa [[NMML|isindi aɣelnaw n temsuṭaṭ tiwlalin Amrikan]] yefkad asazel ɣef tzukt teɣzi-ynes 30 m s ugar n 180 n iṭunnen, ma d tazmek meqqren yakk i d-tuzen s talɣa tufrint Tella d [[tawtemt]] azuk-is yessaweṭ ɣer 177 n iṭunnen.<ref name="pop"/>

